{"tid":537211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國村委會選舉, 公安持槍在旁監視投票者","createTime":"2018-01-22T13:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T16:06:09.000Z","uid":53705,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"164e5f5fce932381e7e741097a65a1bb439d2ee7","tid":537211,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T13:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/aHgrkt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FaHgrkt.jpg&h=06cd797e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山東省濟寧市盧營村村委會換選舉時，網上流傳兩名手持槍支的警察站在一個投票箱兩旁的相片。(網上圖片，拍攝日期不詳) <br />\n<br />\n山東省近日進行基層換屆選舉，其中濟寧市有村莊在選舉期間，有手持槍支的警察站在票箱兩旁，相片在網上流傳引發熱議。熟悉選舉的維權人士質疑，警察是否有需要持槍到現場。（文宇晴報道） <br />\n<br />\n網上流傳一張來自山東省濟寧市盧營村村委會換屆選舉的相片，畫面是兩名手持槍支的警察站在一個投票箱兩旁。有關相片近日在網上引起熱議。 <br />\n<br />\n就有關情況，本台記者嘗試與盧營村的村民聯繫，但至截稿前仍然未能成功。至於盧營村委會以及所屬的柳行街道辦事處的電話，則一直沒有人接聽。"},{"pid":"c515e84b150c12da73949a676ada8725bbe255ee","tid":537211,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T13:57:48.000Z","msg":"垃圾國"},{"pid":"df34d596cef3b1706c975a4bea55bf46c3343621","tid":537211,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:39:04.000Z","msg":"第三世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90904247cb0670ffa194eda9cbc1bd4c99774c44","tid":537211,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c70e02016808f1ff593b339aefd14c1222ef4df","tid":537211,"uid":51828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T14:42:51.000Z","msg":"一條村仔都要搞咁撚多野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7633fa75d893fc10b15b81db9ee4a70977d04e55","tid":537211,"uid":5253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c70e02016808f1ff593b339aefd14c1222ef4df","tid":537211,"uid":51828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0